| `components/workflow/WorkflowHeader.tsx` | Top bar with workflow name, save button, status toggle |

---

## Drag & Drop Flow

1. User drags a node card from the **sidebar**
2. On drop over the canvas, `onDrop` handler creates a new React Flow node at the drop position
3. User connects nodes by dragging from a **source handle** to a **target handle** → creates an edge
4. User clicks **Save** → `POST /api/workflows` with `reactFlowInstance.toObject()`
5. On page load → `GET /api/workflows/{id}` → restore nodes/edges into React Flow

